{"tid":2139426,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大2,500人聯署撐戴耀廷","createTime":"2020-08-04T09:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T04:05:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b3835cff60b4440cd18ad06da8beb705f2a2d0dc","tid":2139426,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:19:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/XINCKHMUCMD5WIVSNLRHQPIE24/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FXINCKHMUCMD5WIVSNLRHQPIE24%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd7uZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=9a2cb44d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FXINCKHMUCMD5WIVSNLRHQPIE24%2F&h=077959a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/XINCKHMUCMD5WIVSNLRHQPIE24/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港大2,500人聯署撐戴耀廷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/X93IeQvdwscAiDJaVy-bY05rxxQ=/190x152/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VYOGHL5HPDNQPQ6INRJJTLELAY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FX93IeQvdwscAiDJaVy-bY05rxxQ%3D%2F190x152%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVYOGHL5HPDNQPQ6INRJJTLELAY.jpg&h=71b0a062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港大學生會昨將收集到的聯署交予教務處以轉交至校長張翔及校委會。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。。。。。港大學生會昨將收集到的聯署交予教務處以轉交至校長張翔及校委會，並指若校委會無視有關訴求，不排除作相應行動，包括要求國際關注。<br />\n<br />\n聯署信向校委會提出以下訴求，分別為撤回解僱戴之決定、本月10日前以書面形式公開推翻教委會建議之理據，以及檢討及修改《香港大學規程》第18條校務委員會中，校委會主席及校外委員的任命程序。港大學生會會長葉芷琳表示，校委會以「違法」作為解僱戴的理由，席間更有人自詡作出「超越學術層面」的決定，公然以政治考量凌駕專業學術判斷，等同向國際社會宣告，校委會已淪中共傀儡。港大發言人回覆指會把港大學生會的函件轉交給校務委員會。<br />\n<br />\n對於近日。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"c00e09091db53367f858dec57241427c276921c7","tid":2139426,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:22:18.000Z","msg":"被嶺大拒終身約申請　葉蔭聰預告明年失